quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,"yɩlg f Sob-zẽkdgã yʋʋrã."
  87,2,"Sẽn naan-ɑ ninsɑɑlã n zems a taabã."
  87,3,"La sẽn kord-a bõn-nɑɑndsã b yɑlẽ gilli, n peeg-bɑ n tʋg sẽn nɑ zems ne-bɑ."
  87,4,"Sẽn yiisd-a yamdã.(rũms wãmneg zĩiga)."
  87,5,"N leb n wa maan-a t'a kʋɩ n sobge."
  87,6,"M na n karmɑ foo tɩ f pa yĩm ye."
  87,7,"Rẽnda bũmb ning Wẽnd sẽn wa n tʋllã; ad Yẽ n mi sẽn vẽnege, la bũmb ning sẽn solge."
  87,8,"La D yols-f ne yol-yole."
  87,9,"Bɩ f tẽeg tɩ tẽegrã sã n nafdẽ."
  87,10,"Ned ning sẽn yaeesd-a nɑ tẽege."
  87,11,"La zu-be-ned zãagd-a lame."
  87,12,"Ning sẽn kẽed bug-kẽengã."
  87,13,"Rẽ poorẽ a pa kiid a pʋgẽ, la a pa vɩɩmsd ye."
  87,14,"Hakɩɩka sẽn yɩlg-a tɩlgame."
  87,15,"La a Tẽeg a Soaba yʋʋr n pʋʋse."
  87,16,"La bala yãmb yɩɩsda dũni vɩɩmã."
  87,17,"La yaoolem raarã sõmb n yɩɩde, n leb n yɩɩd ne paabo."
  87,18,"Ad woto n be rẽenem gaf-rãmbẽ wã."
  87,19,"A ɭbraahɩɩm ne a Musa gaf-rãmbã."
